    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean older vehicle in mint condition and about as nice as you\u2019ll find for its age. It shows extremely little wear inside and out, presents beautifully, and has clearly been very well cared for over time. The interior is tidy and fresh, the exterior has an excellent appearance, and it runs and drives the way a properly maintained example should. If you\u2019ve been looking for a standout older vehicle that needs nothing but a new owner, this is an honest, high-quality example you can feel good about buying.",
