    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. A practical choice for someone seeking an inexpensive daily driver, work car, or project opportunity, it presents an affordable entry point with straightforward appeal. If you\u2019re looking for low-cost mobility without overpaying, this is a compelling option worth a closer look.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest budget car that\u2019s priced for someone who wants affordable wheels or a project with potential. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a straightforward opportunity for a handy buyer looking to save money and put in a little TLC. Great as a fixer-upper, spare vehicle, or something to get you from A to B without spending a fortune. If you appreciate a fair deal and know how to spot value, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-minded driver with the kind of straightforward, easy-to-service mechanical setup enthusiasts appreciate. Starts, runs, and moves out with a willing powertrain, and its simple chassis makes it a great candidate for someone wanting dependable basic transportation or a light project platform. Shows wear consistent with age and use, but that also means you can get into it at an accessible price point without worrying about keeping a show car perfect. If you want an inexpensive car with usable road manners, honest character, and room to improve, this is a compelling buy.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap ride. Rough shape, but it runs and gets the job done. Priced to sell fast.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a machine with stories in its steel and plenty of life left for the right driver. It\u2019s an ideal choice for someone who appreciates a budget-friendly ride with personality, whether you need a practical daily, a weekend tinkering project, or a reliable set of wheels to keep moving. There\u2019s a certain scrappy charm here: turn the key, feel the grit, and imagine the miles still waiting ahead.",
      "price": 6495.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle is a practical opportunity for a handy buyer, first-time owner, or anyone seeking basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for someone comfortable with cosmetic and mechanical needs, but it offers honest value for the money and a chance to get into a vehicle without a major investment. A sensible choice for a project, backup car, or low-cost runabout.",
      "price": 4950.0,
